description.full: This game was classified by the community with the following category scores - Violence=3/3, Sex=3/3, Mature Content=3/3. Meet the Giant Annunaki Princess!  Run errands for her and unlock various carnival activities.  A survival adventure game, surely not for the faint of heart.
